  10 Jan 2006; Benedikt Böhm <hollow@gentoo.org> src/vmount.c:
  Add support for mount flags

  09 Jan 2006; Benedikt Böhm <hollow@gentoo.org> src/vncontext.c:
  Fix netmask handling

  09 Jan 2006; Benedikt Böhm <hollow@gentoo.org> scripts/lib/vps.sh,
  scripts/command/start.sh, scripts/pathconfig.in:
